She ran out with her rifle in her hand and took carefull aim with her 
rifle.  She knealed down and held her breath.  She aimed for Deemos's 
head, and gently squeezed the trigger.

"PHOBIA, HIT THEM WITH EVERYTHING YOU GOT!" she said on her commlink 
to him.  With him in his ship, he would give a lot of firepower to 
dish out.
